WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:03.400
This is my normal Tuesday.

00:00:03.333 --> 00:00:09.733
This is my agent fleet. Eight specialists, one orchestrator. The routing is tested in CI.

00:00:10.700 --> 00:00:17.567
One task in. The orchestrator plans and fans out. Four specialists in parallel,

00:00:18.300 --> 00:00:26.767
each with its own scope and gates. I steered. I didn't type code. It synthesizes, the gates pass.

00:00:26.767 --> 00:00:31.933
It opens the PR. Not a side experiment. It's how every feature ships.

00:00:33.667 --> 00:00:35.833
I ship AI in production.

00:00:35.833 --> 00:00:39.933
In the last six weeks I merged 60+ pull requests

00:00:39.933 --> 00:00:45.733
from frontend to infrastructure, at an average cycle time under 18 hours.

00:00:45.733 --> 00:00:49.133
The fleet writes the migration, the route, the component,

00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:51.300
and the decision record in parallel,

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:54.000
while I review and approve.
